Title: Amends the effectiveness of a chapter of the laws of 2022 amending the insurance law relating to the provision of supplemental spousal liability insurance
Summary: Amends the effectiveness of a chapter of the laws of 2022 amending the insurance law relating to the provision of supplemental spousal liability insurance to persons who are insured for loss resulting from the ownership, maintenance and use of a motor vehicle.
LawCode: Amd ยง2, Chap of 2022 (as proposed in S.9367 & A.1029)
ActClause: AN ACT to amend a chapter of the laws of 2022 amending the insurance law relating to the provision of supplemental spousal liability insurance to persons who are insured for loss resulting from the ownership, maintenance and use of a motor vehicle, as proposed in legislative bills numbers S. 9367 and A. 1029, in relation to the effectiveness thereof
